package Notes
  • Interface Summary
    Interface
    Description
    NoteInterface
    Interface for Note Type Classes (DefaultNote, ChecklistNote, TableNote) (In method descriptions, terms DefaultNote and Default are used interchangeably, same goes with the other types)
    NoteRepository
    This is an interface to manipulate data in the repository, Used by the controller.
